findings.title: Use of Floating Pragma
findings.description: The contract uses a floating pragma version which can lead to unexpected behavior and security vulnerabilities.

findings.title: Potential unauthorized script upgrade
findings.description: The contract may allow an unauthorized user to upgrade the script, potentially leading to unexpected behavior or security vulnerabilities.

findings.title: Minting of unlimited number of sundae tokens
findings.description: The smart contract owner can mint NFTs and add it to the total supply without any limitations.
